{"tid":539002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★19年前大陸結婚 單程證來港定居 倉務員殺妻","createTime":"2018-01-24T07:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T09:48:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e250fad76c1b5b3a75e24af9e61537abc2c66f9","tid":539002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:23:10.000Z","msg":"六旬倉務員疑不甘年輕19載的妻子提出離婚，兩年前在土瓜灣住所內涉嫌徒手勒死對方，並用膠紙封她口鼻，他行兇後到尖沙咀跳海，圖自殺但獲救及被捕，控以一項謀殺罪。<br />\n<br />\n他向警方表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">與妻子19年前在大陸結婚</span>，其後妻子懷孕，<span style=\"color: red;\">偷渡來港產女，之後居於深圳，直至取得單程證來港定居</span>。起初妻子從事美容生意，但因收入欠佳，獲朋友介紹改行推銷保險，客路主要是內地人，她亦因此頻頻北上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/bkn-20180124140639482-0124_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180124%2Fbkn-20180124140639482-0124_00822_001.html&d=ORNTrwOGgTfFwb0C8nnRx0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8f75ef29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/bkn-20180124140639482-0124_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e3c5dcafea8a8981fda91fa71733ce11e5d76795","tid":539002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"專材？"},{"pid":"08a3cf3dcd0e28efccbc219fddb1a50119f76aa7","tid":539002,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"我都黎左香港21年 97年落黎"},{"pid":"a84f083c7fe875625119c3915b724b2c45709d06","tid":539002,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08a3cf3dcd0e28efccbc219fddb1a50119f76aa7","tid":539002,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"我都黎左香港21年 97年落黎"},"cited